   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">To duplicate a section,</p>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Go to Qualifications and Benefits tab of the program.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click Duplicate from the more menu beside the Section Id.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Enter New Start Date and New End Date.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click Add. A new section is created.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click Save.</cmd>
         </step>
      </steps>
      <postreq class="- topic/section task/postreq ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The end date of the existing section is set as follows: </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">End Date of section 1 = (New End Date - 1)</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">For example, if you have an existing section as follows:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">
            <table class="- topic/table ">
               <tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                  <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col3" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col4" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Section Id</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Bundle Name</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Start Date</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">End Date</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">S01</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">B01</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">01 Jan 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">31 Dec 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">If you duplicate the section and enter New Start Date as 01 Jul 2019 and New End Date as 31 Dec 2019, the following section is created:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">
            <table class="- topic/table ">
               <tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                  <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col3" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col4" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Section Id</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Bundle Name</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Start Date</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">End Date</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">S01</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">B01</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">01 Jan 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">30 Jun 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">S02</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">B02</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">01 Jul 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">31 Dec 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">You can now charge a different amount for the second section. To make changes to the bundle amount:</p>
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">Click the expand arrow beside the corresponding section.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Make appropriate changes to the bundle amount or the product amount.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Click<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "> Save. </uicontrol>
